org.svvrl.goal.core.logic.qptl

Class QPTLPastFutureSeparator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.svvrl.goal.core.AbstractAlgorithm
      • org.svvrl.goal.core.logic.qptl.QPTLPastFutureSeparator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.EventListener, Algorithm, AlgorithmListener, FormulaRewriter

    public class QPTLPastFutureSeparator
extends AbstractAlgorithm
implements FormulaRewriter
    This class provides a separation of past and future operators for QPTL formulae that are convertible to prenex normal form.
    Author:
    "Ming-Hsien Tsai"
    See Also:
